      "id": "PopularPost368922",
      "post_content": "The fact that this is black is really what makes it work, this is a blue/red effect in black with a low CMC. The cost is great, ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) is the least color intensive cost that gets the effect. Making a mono-black deck I was looking for a way to fight removal and control decks, this doesn't always work perfectly, but most of the time I lose one to three life and can cost them 2 cards. [Electrolyze](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Electrolyze) is a pain, but [lightning bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lightning bolt) and basically every kill spell fails miserably. [Opportunity](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Opportunity) is hilarious.",
      "posted_by": "Enelysios",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost368922\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_post\">The fact that this is black is really what makes it work, this is a blue/red effect in black with a low CMC. The cost is great, <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> is the least color intensive cost that gets the effect. Making a mono-black deck I was looking for a way to fight removal and control decks, this doesn't always work perfectly, but most of the time I lose one to three life and can cost them 2 cards. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Electrolyze\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Electrolyze\">Electrolyze</a> is a pain, but <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"lightning bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lightning bolt\">lightning bolt</a> and basically every kill spell fails miserably. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Opportunity\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Opportunity\">Opportunity</a> is hilarious.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '368922'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy80532\">Enelysios</span>\r\n               